title: Couple With Heart Man Medium Light Skin Tone Woman Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple, often signifying love, affection, and partnership. This specific variation depicts a woman with a medium-light skin tone and a man with a medium-light skin tone.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the couple with heart emoji, with a man and woman both depicted with medium-light skin tones, offers a warm and loving visual.  The smooth, glossy finish of the surrounding heart and the soft, rounded contours of the couple highlight Apple's refined design aesthetic.  This emoji is a clear symbol of romantic affection, companionship, and shared happiness on Apple devices.
